name: The Fish of Light
description:
Between traces of light emerges a fish created during a boat trip to Tigre, Buenos Aires. Using the lights of the port and the houses in the distance as points of light, through a long exposure, a composition was formed that suggests the shape of a fish. And you, what do you see?
